<P><HI>An&s;wer.</HI> He &s;hould have told what <HI>Books;</HI> for I know of no book formerly of his, (tho' I have &s;een many) wherein he hath Denied that <HI>Doctrine.</HI></P>
<P>But in page 13. of <HI>Shemei,</HI> he Implicitly owns he held it as an Hypothe&s;ys, and then &s;ay's; <HI>Will a Change of mind in that Re|&s;pect prove me to be</HI> varied <HI>in a</HI> Fundamental <HI>&amp;c?</HI></P>
