<P><PB N="8" REF="001143_0009_0FB08C7BAA993660">In page 3. he &s;aith, <HI>I can tell my Voucher told me that <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">e (G. K.) never made it an</HI> Article <HI>of his</HI> <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">aith.</P>
