<P>As for his Accu&s;ing me, in his pa. 4. of a <HI>Notorious Fal&s;|hood,</HI>
<PB N="10" REF="001143_0010_0FB08C7E33D0D0F8">about our difference about eleven years ago, it's fully detected above.</P>
