<PB N="19" REF="001143_0014_0FB08C8D6D674E68"><HI>Some Fundamentals</HI> pa. 10. And indeed, at this rate, he may <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> away any acknowledged <HI>Fundamental,</HI> and yet &s;ay, he is always <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ound, and <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ver varied <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> any <HI>Fundamentals.</HI></P>
